    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.00; tabstops:none;"><tab /><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; vertical-align:baseline; color:#222222; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true">Help and Manual </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true">tool supports all standard help formats ( HTML Help CHM, WebHelp and Visual Studio Help) and creates them all from the same single source, allows multiple users to edit the same project at the same time, provides the ability of </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; vertical-align:baseline; color:#303030;" translate="true">working on groups of related topics without losing track of what you are doing</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true">, provides the automatic translation tools and grammar checkers embedded into the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true">Help and Manual </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true">tool. All the features mentioned above make the</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true"> Help and Manual</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true"> a perfect tool for a group of technical writers working on a big project</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.00; tabstops:none;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.00; tabstops:none;"></para>
