      <li styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.00; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; vertical-align:baseline; color:#222222; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true">the products with similar functionality &#160;</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.00; tabstops:none;"><tab /><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; vertical-align:baseline; color:#222222; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true">It is possible to c</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true">reate libraries of reusable topics and texts, and insert them in projects in the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true">Link</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true"> or </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true">Copy</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true"> mode. In the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true">Link</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true"> mode the texts are updated everywhere they are used when the original files are changed. In the Professional and Server versions you can also reuse topics from other projects directly. Also, i</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; vertical-align:baseline; color:#222222; background-color:#ffffff;" translate="true">t is possible insert a snippet from another topic and </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:12pt; vertical-align:baseline; color:#303030;" translate="true">even create a snippet project to use further in projects describing the similar products</text></para>
